      "post_content": "Fear has not been removed, it's been expanded. Cards like [Fear](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fear) still require a black creature to block it, regardless of the enchanted creature's colors. Intimidate is a different effect, rather than a rewording.",
      "posted_by": "Nerobyrne",
